{"tid":1667814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱睇人討論諗到一招好絕嘅橋，恐怖過同胞勿近","createTime":"2019-10-21T16:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T16:38:52.000Z","uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8896a4af4501072757b5ef7e589371d5ad97fb4e","tid":1667814,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"教人放真假菠蘿呢啲嘢呢，我就唔會叫嘅<br />\n<br />\n因為始終有法律風險，我唔做嘅嘢我唔會叫人做<br />\n<br />\n但係有冇諗過做一個手法嘅好市民幫助警方清理路障呢？<br />\n<br />\n1.首先將一堆磚頭整齊咁棟成一個正方體<br />\n<br />\n2.再用紙皮箱笠住佢<br />\n<br />\n3.上面千祈唔好寫任何嘢因為佢係一個普通紙皮箱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時睇啲藍絲同阿sir咁有型一腳踢開個紙皮箱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日好似有狗踢斷腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除咗笑自己戇鳩你可以告邊個？<br />\n<br />\n又冇人宣稱有炸彈<br />\n又冇人放炸彈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻腳係你自己控制一腳踢落去嘅怪邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314697b645e5e6567d1c37e9379e10c9908551ed","tid":1667814,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:09:05.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係低成本<br />\n<br />\n附近放多幾十個紙箱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢懶一腳踢落去，隻腳就係咁先"},{"pid":"57e4cb9a825b0e3670dc2d5e41de373e503b6342","tid":1667814,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"【文宣學堂】警完美示範「核彈都唔割」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667502</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2199ad72789276e051d248a1b61a208a4608f39","tid":166781